description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Geoffrey transforms KT Tunstall's catchy pop hit "Suddenly I See" with a rhythmically complex Brazilian flair, from his latest solo album Heart of the Piano (2013 - Motéma). Topics covered include dividing rhythmic patterns between the hands, locking in the "groove", harmonizing melodic lines and more! Includes a PDF of the complete note-for-note transcription from the recording. (Level: Advanced)
